            <span class="title"><span class="TextCopy" >Telephony in the Cloud</span></span>
            <p>Twilio provides a cloud API for voice and SMS communications that leverages existing web development skills, resources and infrastructure.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="right_2">
            <span class="title"><span class="TextCopy" >Connect and Coordinate by Phone</span></span>
            <p>Build sales automation systems, order inquiry lines, CRM solutions, interactive SMS apps, call routing apps, phone trees, appointment reminders, custom voicemail apps, and a whole lot more.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="right_3">
            <span class="title"><span class="TextCopy" >Simple, Powerful, Pay As You Go</span></span>
